Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Princes of the Church Live as Princes of the World
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sxcb1
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 May 2002
Alistair Cooke talks about airport security on a war footing; deep vein thrombosis, and how the Roman Catholic church uses canon law to protect its clergy.